        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">The remaining amount of produced ammonia is assumed to leave the production process with the waste water, also the remaining amount of produced ammonia. Further it was assumed that this wastewater is treated in a internal wastewater plant. For the ammonia within the wastewater a removal efficiency of 50% was assumed. The nitrogen emitted to air (N2) and remaining in the sewage sludge was neglected.The remaining amount of ammonia is calculated as ammonia emission to water.</comment>
